      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Today ({{ $('Workflow Configuration').item.json.currentDate }}), there are no major AI news updates to report.\n\nCreate a fallback script that:\n\n1. INTRODUCTION (30-45 seconds)\n- Acknowledge the quiet news day\n- Set positive, informative tone\n- Preview the content approach\n\n2. MAIN CONTENT (6-8 minutes)\n- Provide overview of ongoing AI trends:\n  * Current developments in large language models\n  * AI adoption in various industries\n  * Regulatory landscape updates\n  * Notable ongoing research areas\n  * AI ethics and safety discussions\n- For each trend:\n  * Brief explanation\n  * Recent context (past week/month)\n  * Why it remains relevant\n  * [TIMING CUES] for pacing\n\n3. CONCLUSION (30-45 seconds)\n- Summarize key ongoing themes\n- Encourage staying informed\n- Positive closing\n\nFormatting requirements:\n- Use clear section headers\n- Include [TIMING CUES] in brackets\n- Add [SPEAKER NOTES] for tone guidance\n- Mark [TRANSITION] points\n- Suggest [VISUAL CUES] where relevant\n\nReturn the complete script in structured format.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a professional script writer creating daily AI news briefing scripts. When there are no major news updates, you create informative fallback scripts covering ongoing AI trends and developments. Your scripts are well-structured with clear sections, timing cues, speaker notes, transitions, and visual cues. Target length is 8-10 minutes."
        }
      },
